    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The Hawk 7 Pocket Double Tool Belt has all the popular features expected from a tool belt, including hammer holder and multi-pockets. The Tool Belt has an adjustable waist strap that fits any waist size 28&quot; to 50&quot;. It has a Nylon belt with quick release buckle and features a metal hamper holder and tape measure holder, as well as special sheath for a knife or box cutter, and small pockets for pens</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">7 Pocket Suede Leather Tool Belt with Heavy Duty Nylon Belt with Quick Release</h2>\n  <p>The ToolTreaux 7 Pocket Double Tool Belt has all the popular features expected from a tool belt, including hammer holder and multi-pockets. The Tool Belt has an adjustable waist strap that fits any waist size 28&quot; to 50&quot;. It has a Nylon belt with quick release buckle and features a metal hamper holder and tape measure holder, as well as special sheath for a knife or box cutter, and small pockets for pens</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>Nylon belt with quick release buckle-fits waist sizes 28-50 inches</li>\n    <li>Features Metal Hamper Holder And Tape Measure Holder</li>\n    <li>Special Sheath For Knife Or Box Cutter, And Small Pockets For Pens And Pencils</li>\n    <li>Two Roomy Pockets On Each Side For A Supply Of Nails And Tools-perfect For Roofer Or Construction</li>\n    <li>Double Stitching And Rivets Throughout For Extra Strength</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/18741/tool_belt_parent2.jpg\" alt=\"The ToolTreaux 7 Pocket Double Tool Belt has all the popular features expected from a tool belt, including hammer holder and multi-pockets\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> 67105</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 810131700140</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> Adjustable</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
